comments.body:
> That seems like a bug? Or at least could lead to unexpected results in some configurations.

It's intentional but I understand there are use cases where mirroring would be helpful for more than pulling. Looking at the man page of the [registries.conf](https://github.com/containers/image/blob/master/docs/containers-registries.conf.5.md) I think we should make it more obvious that mirrors are only consulted for pulling.

@mtrmac WDYT?
